// Remote-controlled MCEM-74 (Mobile Combat Engineering & Maintenance) Treadbot

/mob/living/silicon/engibot
	name = "\improper MCEM-74 Treadbot"
	desc = "The MCEM-Treadbot-Series are ruggedized, tracked maintenance drones designed for the high-stress environments of military vessels, currently undergoing field testing. Fitted with a multi-purpose 3-jointed A-8 Hydraulic Manipulator arm, it can perform both repairs, move objects around, and salute superior officers. Thanks to its plasteel chassis, it is also \"hardened\" against the electromagnetic interference of spaceship weaponry and the corrosive atmosphere of damaged reactors. The design philosophy here is quite simple: it doesn't just fix things; it survives the things that break them."
	icon = "icons/mob/robots.dmi"
